<br>
Is this request unreasonable? I would think that if anything this would be a benefit to the SKALD class.<br>
<br>
It would give us a GOOD 2hd weapon with thrust (which until the Savage was introduced only Hunters with SPEARS had any thrust damage weapons).<br>
<br>
Perhaps I'm missing something but would this not be a reasonable request? Would it not also allow for a greater range of possible specs?<br>
<br>
How hard would this be to have Mythic implement? Most of the races that can be skalds can also be Hunters (Troll being the sole exception and perhaps requiring a model to be created for the nifty spear evade move).<br>
<br>
Just shooting this by you and the rest of the community...I know I've made mention of it before on other wishlist type threads, but I was just wondering if this is perhaps something to look into or just somthing that may be out of scope.<br>
<br>
